{"type":"message","id":"e5502da7","parentId":"7667633e","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:49:45.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我：\n1. 爬取今天的 AI 热点（大模型、智能体方向）\n2. 包括微信公众号、互联网产品、竞品公司动态\n3. 将原始数据存入 shared-workspace/daily-intel/2026-03-04-researcher.md\n\n我需要：\n1. 使用 web_fetch 进行搜索引擎查询\n2. 优先使用 multi-search-engine 技能（但根据我的工具列表，没有 multi-search-engine 这个工具，只有 web_search）\n3. 按照数据源分类爬取：AI技术前沿、运营商动态、互联网产品、市场分析\n4. 提取：标题、来源、发布时间、链接\n5. 保存到指定路径\n\n首先检查 shared-workspace/daily-intel/ 目录是否存在，然后开始爬取。\n\n由于我之前已经爬取过一次，但用户要求存到不同的路径（shared-workspace/daily-intel/），我需要：\n1. 确认目录存在\n2. 重新爬取或整理之前的爬取数据\n3. 按照要求的数据格式存储\n\n让我先检查目录是否存在，然后进行爬取。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我现在开始爬取今天的 AI 热点数据，并存储到 `shared-workspace/daily-intel/2026-03-04-researcher.md`。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-89ddfd41979f4de2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/shared-workspace/daily-intel"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":19464,"output":309,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772603376618}}
